parameters.name: taskIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the export task.

nested_items.name: graphId
nested_items.description: The source graph identifier of the cancelled export task.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the IAM role that will allow the exporting of data to the destination.

nested_items.name: taskId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the export task.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current status of the export task. The status is CANCELLING when the export task is cancelled.

nested_items.name: format
nested_items.description: The format of the cancelled export task.

nested_items.name: destination
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 URI of the cancelled export task where data will be exported to.

nested_items.name: kmsKeyIdentifier
nested_items.description: The KMS key identifier of the cancelled export task.

nested_items.name: parquetType
nested_items.description: The parquet type of the cancelled export task.

nested_items.name: statusReason
nested_items.description: The reason that the export task has this status value.
